        "action": "Make training on climate change science available to MPs",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Climate change is the biggest threat faced by the world today. In the UK it is not taken seriously enough by the legislature partly because not all MPs have sufficient scientific literacy. Formal training sessions for all MPs provided by climate scientists could greatly improve this situation.",
